        "body": "1. Start with a plain edge between an answer-bearing object and an open question.\n2. If the source really resolves the target, assign `planning.answers`.\n3. Leave the base edge valid and let the class provide meaning and defaults.\n4. Override styling only when the local graph needs a special emphasis.",
